data.title: 'Meche' Carreño, Mexican film actress, dies at 74
data.meta_description: On Friday afternoon, the death of actress' Meche 'Carreño, who was admitted to a hospital three days ago, was reported dead.
data.text:
Mexican cinema transgressor icon 'Meche' Carreño dies

Mercedes' Meche 'Carreño, a Mexican actress and screenwriter famous for her protagonists naked, violence and themes such as abortion and infidelity, died this Friday at the age of 74. The family confirmed the death to TV Azteca, which occurred in a hospital in the United States due to complications related to liver cancer.Continue reading
